########################################################################
##                                                                    ##
##      Instructions on using "lxplus-setup" on the CERN cluster      ##
##                                                                    ##
########################################################################

1. To create a master directory for the h_bbg process run:
	 (1a) Adjust the name of the master directory in "setup.sh" script
	 (1b) Adjust the desired output directory in "setup.sh" script
	 (1c) Adjust master input card "powheg.input-save" inside "cards/" directory
	 (1d) Run: ./setup.sh

2. Enter newly created master directory and follow instructions therein
